# Raw scrape (268 MB source of truth for the snapshot). The derived
# artifacts (snapshot/parquet/, snapshot/scrape_index.json, audit_full.json)
# ARE committed so the repo is self-contained and reproducible.
#
# v3.1.0 also commits the tabular source folders (~94 MB) so read_resource
# works fully offline on non-DataStore XLSX/XLS/CSV files. The non-tabular
# scrape folders (PDFs, images, DOCX, GeoJSON, ODS, XML, WORD) remain
# ignored — they're ~174 MB and not queryable anyway.
agridata_TN_Scraped_*/format_pdf/
agridata_TN_Scraped_*/format_jpeg/
agridata_TN_Scraped_*/format_png/
agridata_TN_Scraped_*/format_docx/
agridata_TN_Scraped_*/format_word/
agridata_TN_Scraped_*/format_geojson/
agridata_TN_Scraped_*/format_ods/
agridata_TN_Scraped_*/format_xml/
agridata_TN_Scraped_*/Master_Climate_Data_Stitched.csv
agridata_TN_Scraped_*/TanitData_Solar_Map_*.html
agridata_TN_Scraped_*/TanitData_Stitching_Map.csv

