# NOTE v3.0.0: audit_full.json and snapshot/ are now intentionally TRACKED.
# audit_full.json cannot be regenerated while the portal is down and is
# the single source of truth for catalog metadata in snapshot mode.
# snapshot/parquet/ is deterministic given the scrape + audit; we commit
# it so clones are self-contained without needing the 268 MB scrape.
